This course requires submission of analytic response papers (2-3 pages each) on
four of the plays read or attended; a theatrical scene, with dialogue (3-
5 pages); and a major paperÂ (PDF).Â There is also a final exam.Â In addition,
during the latter half of the course, students are required to lead the
discussion of one play, and to perform in a scene from it as part of that
process. They must also give a brief (5-minute) presentation based on the
research paper, sharing their most interesting insights with the class.
